    "MissionTokens": {
        "Contractor|BountyFPSTitle": [
            "Bounty Extraction: [TargetName] (MRT)"
        ],
        "Contractor|BountyFPSDescription": [
            "Seems we have a good opportunity to make everyone in Crusader a little bit safer today. \n\nWe just received intel that a criminal by the name of [TargetName] (who has been causing a fair bit of mayhem) has been tracked to [Location|Address]. [Location|CaveSize] \n\nNow, they most likely will have others holed up there with them. Deal with them if you have to, but remember that your target is [TargetName|Last].\n\nCONTRACT AUTHORIZED BY:\nLiaison Officer Bautista\nID# 948J030K",
            "Crusader, in accordance with UEE Law, has issued a bounty for [TargetName]. You are charged with apprehending this criminal from their hideout at [Location|Address]. [Location|CaveSize]\n\nPlease be careful entering the site as [TargetName|Last] may not be alone.\n\nCONTRACT AUTHORIZED BY:\nLiaison Officer Bautista\nID# 948J030K",
            "After a long search, we have finally been able to track down a long-wanted criminal, [TargetName], to [Location|Address]. You have been authorized to enter the site, find them, and resolve the bounty. [Location|CaveSize]\n\nUnfortunately, there is a good chance that [TargetName|Last] will not be alone. Be ready to use force if needed. \n\nIt will probably be needed.\n\nCONTRACT AUTHORIZED BY:\nLiaison Officer Gibbs\nID# 91G66BW0",
            "Crusader, in accordance with UEE Law, has issued a bounty for [TargetName] who is currently believed to be hiding at [Location|Address]. \n\nWe need you to infiltrate the site, bypass any armed associates that [TargetName|Last] may have, and apprehend them. [Location|CaveSize]\n\nCONTRACT AUTHORIZED BY:\nLiaison Officer Gibbs\nID# 91G66BW0"
        ],
        "Contractor": [
            "Crusader Security"
        ]
    },
